name: Fish Head Izakaya
description:
“Fish Head” Izakaya, it’s a japanese secret bar which is only known to a group of Japanese elderly people.

If you accidentially get into this bar, the Fish Head employee will definitely serve you with delicated foods and beverages. All the foods are cooked from good quality seaweed and craft beer called “Asasea”.

Asasea is a salted beer, the special salt is extracted from sauna-steamed tuna skin. You will get a saltiness from your mouth to your deepest taste palette. You will feel like you’re diving in the deep blue sea and finally fall asleep. That’s because the bar will drop a pinch of “memory-erasing sleeping pills” into the foods, and the employee will then call “Crab car” taxi services to bring you back home safely.
So as to keep the bar secret!

This is the best picture from the picture book called “Fish Head”.
I’m glad to invite all the Whales to visit the Fish Head Secret bar.
